node.text:
Giving back is something that ROKiT takes great pride in. ROKiT Cities is delivering WiFi connectivity for the residents of Community First! Village, providing affordable, permanent housing, and a supportive community for 200 men and women coming out of chronic homelessness. The connectivity is enabled over installed carrier-grade ROKiT hardware – providing residents with internet access and WiFi calling, ROKiT’s vast 3D movies library, music streaming and more, wherever they are in the 51-acre community. To find out more, check out this short video:
@mobileloaves #keeptalking #ROKiTPhonesUK #3Dsmartphones #wificities #ServingGoodness

node.title: ROKiT Cities installs Free WiFi to Community First! Village in Austin

node.text: Today on our WB virtual tour, we visit New York St, which has been a part of Warner Bros. Studios for almost 100 years. This legendary street has transformed from Gotham City to a futuristic LA in Blade Runner, and so much more. We teamed up with @wbtourhollywood last year to shoot this footage, and are excited to share it with you while the tour is temporarily closed. Watch it now in 3D, as well as other exciting content when you purchase a ROKiT Phone starting at just $89 at rokitphones.com! #ROKiT #ROKiTPhones 🎬 #ROKiT

node.text: While tours are temporarily closed, we wanted to bring a little bit of the Warner Bros. Studio Tour home to you. Welcome to the first episode of our virtual tour! Last year, we teamed up with @wbtourhollywood to capture some footage of their most memorable tour stops. Let’s begin with a look at the WB soundstages. And if you have a ROKiT 3D Phone, you can watch it on ROKiT FLiX 3D now!  #ROKiT #ROKiTPhones
